highlights.text: XXXTENTACION has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “SAD!” is the highest at #33.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 108 weeks straight.
“MIDDLE CHILD” by J. Cole is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 109 spots at #2.
“Swan Song - From the Motion Picture "Alita: Battle Angel"” by Dua Lipa is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #31.
